responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "7967D7FC49E8AC29829DD098F333FDF5", "I\'m not sure what\'s causing the unrest, but we\'ve been finding a lot of bones among the stones as we excavate. Perhaps my efforts to uncover the carvings are stirring up the spirits of this place, or mayhap it\'s the efforts of that Hornersharp fellow, his workers have no respect for the history we\'re uncovering here! Either way, you\'re right that something must be done.")
